Title: ðŸ’°ðŸ’²[250,000,000 IX ][X-Block][BOUNTY]The first global Blockchain 4.0ðŸ’²ðŸ’°
Body: As an outstanding representative of public chains in the era of Blockchain 4.0, X-Block is the first global public chain built on the Fog computing framework, which aims at creating a user-friendly, convenient and open light eco-blockchain.  Relying on the Fog computing framework, X-Block can utilize various heterogeneous devices (including personal computers, smartphones, routers, etc.) to form a decentralized computing engine. By creatively designing the â€œGalaxy Super-Contractâ€, it enables the smart contract to maximally invoke the powerful Fog computing proprietary technology. Meanwhile, computing resources of the surrounding idle equipment can be integrated via X-Block. This will further empower the blockchain to be integrated into everyday technological processes. Such as artificial intelligence, big data and Internet of Things. Thus, a disrupting smart blockchain era can be ushered in to deeply promote applications of blockchain technology in day-to-day life.  X-Block is committed to the construction of a complete blockchain ecosystem and X-Block has built X-Change along with X-Blockâ€™s fog computing and blockchain tools to accomplish the token ecosystem. X-Change is a community-autonomous exchange that incorporates X-Block tokens with trading and mining.   We invite you to participate in our bounty campaign. X-Block team is offering up to 250,000,000 tokens. At present, we set 1 stake= 1 token.    1.Original Video   Attention! Campaign is closed for new participants! Do Original Videoï¼Œyou can obtain 100~3000 stakes every video. â€¢ 100-999 followersï¼š100 stakes â€¢ 1000-4999 followersï¼š800 stakes â€¢ 5000-9999 followersï¼š1500 stakes â€¢ 10001+ followersï¼š3000 stakes NOTE: The task can be performed up to 1 time every two days. 2.Follow Us On Youtube Take the task of following X-Block Official Page on Youtubeï¼Œupload the screenshot ,you can obtain 100 stakes. X-Block Official Youtubeï¼šYOUTUBE NOTE: The task can be performed up to 1 time before the end of ICO. 3. Upvote on YoutubeAttention! Campaign is closed for new participants! Take the task of Upvote X-Block Official video on Youtubeï¼Œupload the screenshot ,you can obtain 50 stakes every video. X-Block Official Youtubeï¼šYOUTUBE NOTE: The task can be performed up to 1 time every official video.    1.Youtube videos must be at least 2 minutes long. You must have at least 100 organic subscribers. 2.All video names need to include X-Block, Blockchain. 3.The video description or content needs to mention the project name X-Block, the project official website x-block.io, the project telegram group link t.me/XblockOfficial, introduce the advantages of the project, and the video maker's own understanding of the X-Block project. (about 50words) 4.Video cannot be deleted before the project is raised, otherwise the stakes will not be rewarded. 5.A maximum of 1 video every two days 6.All released videos need to authorize X-Block official use and forwarding permissions. 7.Video needs to be original. Users found copying other videos will be disqualified. 8.This is a high quality project, and we encourage genuine discussion and opinions. Any misrepresentations of the project/ false claims will not be permitted and stakes will not be awarded.    1.Bitcointalk Avatar&Text Wear our avatar and personal textï¼Œyou can obtain 5~40 stakes a week. â€¢ Junior Member : 50 stakes â€¢ Member: 100 stakes â€¢ Full Member: 150 stakes â€¢ Sr. Member: 250 stakes â€¢ Hero Member : 350 stakes â€¢ Legendary: 400 stakes You can get Avatar from here:AVATAR Personal text: X-Block.io NOTE: The task can be performed up to 1 time everyweek.   1.Participants have to be at least Jr. Member. 2.Every participant must wear our avatar and personal text. And must be kept until the stakes have been calculated after the end of every week, otherwise you will not receive token rewards. 3.Multiple accounts will be banned if spotted. Spam is not allowed. If itâ€™s foundï¼Œparticipants will be banned from any other bounty campaign. 4.Make at least 15 posts each week during the week, at least in 5 different days.If you don't reach 15 posts before a Wednesday, you will not receive any stake for the current week. 5.Posts with less than 80 characters will not be counted as valid posts. 6.Do not post without wearing our signature, or you will be rejected. 7.We will single handedly check every post of every participant. 8.Red trust accounts are not allowed to join this campaign. If you receive red trust while on the campaign, you will be kicked.   Invite friends to register bounty campaign, friends finish registration on official website x-block.io, you can obtain 50 and more stakes. â€¢ Inviter gets 50 stakes/person â€¢ Invitee joined the campaign, inviter gets 5% from the rewarded stakes (rewarded by doing activities) of invitee. NOTEï¼š Friends should not registered bounty campaign You can share directly with friends or copy links to friends. Our system can automatically recognize that you have invited this friend.   1. Follow and like Facebook Follow and like X-Block official Facebook, upload the screenshot, you can obtain 100 stakes. X-Block Facebook Link: FACEBOOK NOTE: The task can be performed up to 1 time before the end of ICO. 2. Reply the post on Facebook Attention! Campaign is closed for new participants! Reply the X-Block official post within 4 days on Facebookï¼Œupload the screenshot, you can obtain 50 stakes every reply. X-Block Facebook Link: FACEBOOK NOTE: The task can be performed up to 2 times everyday. 3. Share on Facebook NEW! Share X-Block posts on Facebook; Submit a reply contains your shared facebook links to our bitcointalk thread; by upload bitcointalk reply link to bounty campaign site, you will be rewarded 400 stakes per week. X-Block Facebook Link: FACEBOOK NOTE: This task is on weekly basis You can get your Bitcointalk post link by clicking the #number at the upper right corner of your bitcointalk post Your facebook share posts must not be deleted until X-Block ICO ends or X-Block official notification whichever comes first During the week, you must share at least 5 posts but not exceeding 10 posts of your Facebook account Maximum 2 posts shared per day Use your own links while uploading to us, X-block has zero tolerance with piracy Do not share ALL posts in one day   1.Participants must follow and like X-Blockâ€™s Facebook page: FACEBOOK 2.Facebook accounts must be original. Fake, dead, inactive and bot accounts will not be accepted. 3.Joining with multiple accounts is not allowed. Users found to be using multi accounts will be disqualified. 4.Terms and conditions can be changed or more can be applied. 5.The username mustnâ€™t contain such words as â€œICOâ€, â€œbountyâ€, â€œbounty hunterâ€, â€œcryptocurrencyâ€ and so on. The avatar must contain your real photo. The number of your posts mustn't exceed 100 per week. Otherwise you will be disqualified. If you are caught in following back youâ€™ll be immediately banned.    Original Articles Post Original Articlesï¼Œyou can obtain 1000~20000 stakes every articles. â€¢ 100-1000 followersï¼šrejected- 0 stake; accept- 1000 stakes â€¢ 1001-10000 followersï¼šrejected-0 stake; accept- 2000 stakes â€¢ 10001-100000 followersï¼šrejected- 0 stake; accept- 4000stakes â€¢ 100001-500000 followersï¼šrejected-0 stake; accept- 8000 stakes â€¢ 500001+followers:rejected-0 stake; accept- 20000 stakes. NOTE: The task can be performed up to 1 time everyday.   1.Your article has to be of a high standard and grammatically correct. 2.Medium and tumblr will be accepted. 3.The article label needs to contain at least 3 labels as follows: #XBlock, #Blockchain, #Crypto, #ether, #ethereum, #bitcoin ,#cryptocurrency ,#ICO , #tokensale 4.You must be followed by at least 100 users 5.1 per day maximum. It must be 500 words long or more. 6.Your article must be unique. It CANNOT be a copied and pasted article. Video needs to be original. Otherwise users will be disqualified. 7.It must be written in English. 8.Articles need to paste the following official links: Websiteï¼šhttps://x-block.io/ Telegramï¼št.me/XblockOfficial Twitterï¼šhttps://twitter.com/XBlockOfficial 9.The author of the article should review the official documentation to ensure an accurate description of the x-block. 10.Articles need to describe the advantages of the X-Block. 11.Articles should be posted on any open access website 12.We reserve the right to consider any article not eligible for this campaign, without giving any reason.   1.Follow Us On Twitter Take the task of following X-Block Official Page on TWITTERï¼Œyou can obtain 400 stakes. 2. Retweet On Twitter Retweet any tweets of X-Block Official twitter within 4 days, you can obtain 75~600 stakes. â€¢ 50-100 Followersï¼š75 stakes â€¢ 101-2000 Followersï¼š150 stakes â€¢ 2001+ Followersï¼š300 stakes NOTE: The task can be performed up to 2 times everyday.   1.Follow X-Block on Twitterï¼šTWITTER 2.Only twitter accounts with more than 50 followers will be allowed. 3.Do not RT and like tweets that are answers to other users. 4.Tweets/retweets, participants need to take the stakes immediately, otherwise it may be unsuccessful. 5.RT should add at least 2 of these hashtags #XBlock #Blockchain #Crypto #ether #ethereum #bitcoin #cryptocurrency #ICO #tokensale 6.Do not RT and like tweets that are more than four days old. 7.Your twitter audit (https://www.twitteraudit.com/) score must be equal to at least 85% and only real followers from the last audit will count. 8.We reserve the right to not consider your twitter account eligible for this campaign, even if you meet the prerequisites.   Translation Translate our ANN and Whitepaper and proofreadingï¼Œyou can obtain 240~4000 stakes. â€¢ ANNï¼ˆincludes campaignï¼‰translationï¼š800 stakes â€¢ ANN proofreadingï¼š240 stakes â€¢ Whitepaper translationï¼š 4000 stakes â€¢ Whitepaper proofreadingï¼š 1200 stakes X-Block Whitepaper Linkï¼šhttps://x-block.io/xblockfile/X-blockWhitepaper.pdf NOTE: Pls read the Rules.    1.Translation includesï¼šWhitepaper: https://x-block.io/xblockfile/X-blockWhitepaper.pdf ï¼ŒANN 2.We will ask you to translate our ANN thread and moderate it until the end of the program. We also expect you to translate whitepaper. 3.We expect text to be written and proofread by humans, the translation must be of a high qualityï¼Œif we find out you've used automation tools to provide the translation (e.g. Google Translate), you will be banned from the campaign as a whole. 4.One person can only choose one language to translate. 5.Do not distort the meaning of texts and publications. 6.Do not distort the essence or structure. Information must be fully translated. 7.Local language should be updated regularly. Track the updated content in the source official file, otherwise the reward amount will be reduced 8.We are only looking for translations in the following languages: Japanese, Korean, Chinese, Vietnamese, Spanish, French, Italian, Dutch, Russian, Portuguese, Indonesian, Hindi, Arabic. 9.Once you have reserved an ANN thread translation, this reservation is valid for 2 days. 10.Once you have reserved a whitepaper translation, this reservation is valid for 7 days. 11.If you cannot complete the task within the time given to you, we will assign a new translator.   1.Follow Us On Reddit Take the task of following X-Block Official Page on redditï¼Œupload the screenshotï¼Œyou can obtain 100 stakes. Redditï¼šREDDIT 2.Upvote On RedditAttention! Campaign is closed for new participants! Upvote any post of X-Block Official reddit within 4 days, upload the screenshot, you can obtain 20 stakes. NOTE: The task can be performed up to 2 times everyday.    Spread in Telegram Spread the content in your Telegram group about X-Block and upload the screenshot to earn some tokens. â€¢ 100-249 membersï¼š10 stakes/ post â€¢ 250-749 membersï¼š15 stakes/ post â€¢ 750-2499 membersï¼š20 stakes/ post â€¢ 2500+membersï¼š30 stakes/ post NOTEï¼š Up to 1000 tokens per week per account 'Spread Contentâ€˜ï¼š X-Block is the first global public chain built on the Fog computing framework, which aims at creating a user-friendly, convenient and open light Eco-Blockchain. Website: https://x-block.io/ Telegramï¼š t.me/XblockOfficial Twitter: https://twitter.com/XBlockOfficial Medium: https://medium.com/@xblockofficial Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/XBlockChain/    1.Spread the content in your Telegram group about X-Block and earn some tokens 2.A maximum of 1 post every two days is allowed in each group (this rules is required, because audience wonâ€™t accept daily spam in good channel what is bad for advertising value). 3.You must Stay in the group until the end of ICO to receive your stakes. 4.Upload the screenshot (gif,jpg,jpeg,bmp,png) and report it in our website    1.Picture reward â€¢ fail to auditï¼š0 stakeï¼› â€¢ successful audit: 30 stake/picture 2.GIF reward fail to auditï¼š0 stakeï¼› successful audit: 60 stake/gif   1.Make creative pictures and creative GIFs related to X-Block. 2.All pictures and GIFs need to authorize X-Block use permissions. 3.10 pictures and 10 GIFs per day maximum, which means every person can upload 20 photos per day. 4.You need to use email to register on the official website https://x-block.io/ to participate in this campaign. 5.You should send pictures to X-Block official telegram( t.me/XblockOfficial) administrator @Sarahx05 through telegram, and tell her your bounty email address at the same time, the administrator will record your reward for you. Author: toilatin2003
Title: ðŸ’°ðŸ’²[250,000,000 IX ][X-Block][BOUNTY]The first global Blockchain 4.0ðŸ’²ðŸ’°
Body: With its ingenious consensus mechanism, BTC X-Block has created a public chain that lowers the participation threshold of Blockchain Technology, creating a network that allows all types of devices to join and contribute their computing resources. In order to realize the goal of Fog computing, the overhead of consensus must be reduced to a minimum, while maintaining speed and efficiency. This allows X-Block to have rapid allocation of resources across the network in a secure and tamper-proof way.  BTC The final evolution of our technology will usher in a new era of distributed computing.  Currently, a large portion of all data processed on the internet is handled by cloud computing providers, and is therefore susceptible to all the negatives of centralized data services. X-Block will provide distributed computing to developers and businesses ,  with the benefits of complete transparency, geo-redundancy, and total privacy. X-Block is creating a supercomputer that is made of consumer hardware, for use by anyone.

Being a linguist, so I guarantee you a professionally done translation without stylistic, grammatical and lexicological mistakes. I constantly improve my expertise by reading the specialized literature. I never miss the deadlines and I will provide you with the translation according to your terms and requirements. Body: What is X-Block ? â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”   As an outstanding representative of public chains in the era of Blockchain 4.0, X-Block is the first global public chain built on the Fog computing framework, which aims at creating a user-friendly, convenient and open light eco-blockchain.  Relying on the Fog computing framework, X-Block can utilize various heterogeneous devices (including personal computers, smartphones, routers, etc.) to form a decentralized computing engine. By creatively designing the â€œGalaxy Super-Contractâ€, it enables the smart contract to maximally invoke the powerful Fog computing proprietary technology. Meanwhile, computing resources of the surrounding idle equipment can be integrated via X-Block. This will further empower the blockchain to be integrated into everyday technological processes. Such as artificial intelligence, big data and Internet of Things. Thus, a disrupting smart blockchain era can be ushered in to deeply promote applications of blockchain technology in day-to-day life.  X-Block is committed to the construction of a complete blockchain ecosystem and X-Block has built X-Change along with X-Blockâ€™s fog computing and blockchain tools to accomplish the token ecosystem. X-Change is a community-autonomous exchange that incorporates X-Block tokens with trading and mining.
